project_descr: Blue Ribbon Commission II: 2d Wave of Reforms in Ukraine

outputs.output_descr: The project is designed to support next generation of economic reforms in Ukraine. It intends to use Blue Ribbon Commission Reports, as well as national strategic planninig documents and the EU-Ukraine Action Plan as the platform to mobilize wide range of national and international communities in supporting the Ukrainian policy stakeholders to implement reforms.

project_title: blue ribbon commission ii: 2d wave of reforms in ukraine
